channel.title: Gmod
channel.description:
Theres a something going on with my Gmod. Whenever i shoot a gun i downloaded the shell cases come out as big ERROR signs. It was not doing this the last time i played and i haven't downloaded anything since then.
Any idea on what could be wrong would be greatly appreciated.

item.title: Gmod
item.dc:creator: Zeus
item.description:
BlackWing94:

the shell cases come out as big ERROR signs

The particle effect that the shells are (shells are not props, but particle FX) is missing or being mis-referenced. Try reinstalling the addon, and if that doesn’t work, then it’s the fault of the code, not your game.
